<div class="heroContainer">
  <div class="bottomLayer">
    <img class="heroOne" src="./images/TableThree.jpg">
  </div>
  <div class="topLayer">
    {{#if loggedIn}}
      <div class="search">
        <input id="searchBar" type="text" placeholder="Find a Restaurant... (Try something like 'Taco')">
        <div id="searchClear" class="hidden">X</div>
        <div id="searchBtn" class="hidden">Go</div>
        <script src="./js/searchHandler.js"></script>
      </div>
    {{else}}
      <div class="entryLinks">
        <a href="/signup" class="button1">Sign Up</a>
        <p>|</p>
        <a href="/login" class="button1">Login</a>
      </div>
    {{/if}}
  </div>


  <svg id="arrow" x="0px" y="0px" width="960px" height="560px" viewBox="0 0 960 560">
    <g>
      <path id="arrowPath" d="M480,344.181L268.869,131.889c-15.756-15.859-41.3-15.859-57.054,0c-15.754,15.857-15.754,41.57,0,57.431l237.632,238.937   c8.395,8.451,19.562,12.254,30.553,11.698c10.993,0.556,22.159-3.247,30.555-11.698l237.631-238.937   c15.756-15.86,15.756-41.571,0-57.431s-41.299-15.859-57.051,0L480,344.181z" />
    </g>
  </svg>

  <card>
    <div class="inner">
      <h2>About:</h2>
      <p>Our team works with restaurants to make the reservation process easy! Each location has a floor plan laid out
        so you can choose exactly where you want to sit. Book directly through us and manage your reservation
        through your account.</p>
    </div>
  </card>

  <card class="right">
    <div class="inner">
      <h2>How to:</h2>
      <p>Log in or create an account with us by following the link above. After logging in you're able to search for
        participating restaurants, view their tables availible for reservation and make requests for whichever table
        looks best!</p>
    </div>
  </card>
</div>